msgid ""
"The attended sysupgrade service allows to easily upgrade vanilla and custom "
"firmware images."
msgstr ""
"Ligeann an tseirbhís sysupgrade ar fhreastail sé ar íomhánna fanaile agus "
"firmware saincheaptha a uasghrádú go héasca."

